      "author": "RuanPienaarCode",
      "description": "First public release of Budget Vault — a personal budget dashboard that reads and writes plain markdown files in your own vault.\n\n**Views:** dashboard, transactions, budgets, savings, accounts, owed money, services, tax, and CSV statement import.\n\n**Highlights**\n- Your data stays yours — plain markdown in a folder you choose, no account, no upload, no network requests of any kind.\n- Works on desktop and mobile (iOS and Android).\n- First-run setup wizard scaffolds the folder structure; an existing budget folder is adopted as-is.\n- Country profiles (South Africa, US, UK, Eurozone, Australia, Canada, Other) drive currency formatting, statement date order, bank import hints, and the whole tax view vocabulary.\n\n**Install manually:** copy `main.js`, `manifest.json` and `styles.css` into `<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/budget-app/`, then enable the plugin in Settings → Community plugins.",
